text:
Tulasee Bio-Ethanol Stock Soars to All-Time High, Signaling Industry Dominance
Tulasee Bio-Ethanolachieved an all-time high stock price on November 6, 2025, reflecting its strong performance in the commodity chemicals sector. The company has significantly outperformed industry peers and demonstrated impressive year-over-year growth, maintaining a consistent upward trend in its trading averages despite some erratic patterns.
Tulasee Bio-Ethanolhas reached a significant milestone, hitting an all-time high of Rs. 69.82 on November 6, 2025. This achievement underscores the company's robust performance in the commodity chemicals sector, particularly as it has outperformed its industry peers by 2.46% today.
The stock has shown impressive momentum, gaining 4.02% over the last two days and reflecting a remarkable 288.10% increase over the past year, significantly surpassing the Sensex's 3.79% growth during the same period. Year-to-date,
Tulasee Bio-Ethanolhas delivered a staggering 292.25% return, further solidifying its position in the market.
Additionally, the stock has consistently traded above its 5-day, 20-day, 50-day, 100-day, and 200-day moving averages, indicating a strong upward trend. Despite some erratic trading patterns, with no trades on two days out of the last 20, the overall performance metrics highlight Tulasee Bio-Ethanol's resilience and growth trajectory in the competitive landscape.
